        <p>
          SendMail provides an email marketing platform that allows you to create, send, and manage email campaigns, build subscriber lists, and analyze campaign performance.
        </p>

        <h2>Account Registration</h2>
        <p>To use our services, you must:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate and complete registration information</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
          <li>Be at least 18 years old or have legal authority to enter into agreements</li>
          <li>Not share your account with unauthorized users</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Acceptable Use Policy</h2>
        <p>You agree not to use SendMail to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Send spam or unsolicited bulk email</li>
          <li>Distribute malware, phishing attempts, or fraudulent content</li>
          <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
          <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights</li>
          <li>Send emails to purchased, rented, or harvested lists</li>
          <li>Harass, abuse, or harm others</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Email Compliance</h2>
        <p>You must comply with all applicable email laws, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>CAN-SPAM Act (USA)</li>
          <li>GDPR (European Union)</li>
          <li>POPIA (South Africa)</li>
          <li>Other applicable anti-spam legislation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This includes obtaining proper consent, providing unsubscribe mechanisms, and honoring opt-out requests.</p>

        <h2>Billing and Payment</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Paid plans are billed in advance on a monthly or annual basis</li>
          <li>Prices are subject to change with 30 days notice</li>
          <li>Refunds are not provided for partial billing periods</li>
          <li>We may suspend accounts with overdue payments</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Service Availability</h2>
        <p>
          We strive to maintain high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Scheduled maintenance will be communicated in advance when possible.
        </p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          You retain ownership of your content and subscriber data. You grant us a license to use this data solely to provide our services. SendMail and its branding are our intellectual property.
        </p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          SendMail is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of our services.
        </p>

        <h2>Termination</h2>
        <p>
          Either party may terminate the agreement at any time. We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms. Upon termination, your right to use the service ceases immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of Zimbabwe. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Zimbabwe.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@sendmail.co.zw">legal@sendmail.co.zw</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
